        },
        {
            "title": "歐盟將暫緩對930億歐元美國商品加徵反制關稅的計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在川普收回對部分反對其獲得格陵蘭的歐盟國家加徵關稅的威脅後，歐盟將把對價值930億歐元（約合1090億美元）美國商品的報復性關稅再度推遲六個月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟委員會發言人Olof Gill表示，該委員會計畫提交一項提案，延長原定於2月7日到期的反制措施暫停期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Gill周五在布魯塞爾對記者表示，「我們通過外交和政治手段實現了目標，這始終是我們的首選，而不是陷入措施與反制措施的螺旋。」他說，暫停期將持續六個月，但如有需要，反制措施可在任何時候重新啟動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a53d7053-2951-3a23-808c-0f2e6dddd22e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普此前在格陵蘭問題上的強硬做派導致局勢緊張，促使歐盟領導人也提出可能動用反脅迫工具這一最強有力的貿易工具來應對美國，而歐洲議會也一度暫停批准歐盟與美國的貿易協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲議會議長Roberta Metsola周四在歐盟領導人峰會前對記者表示，歐洲議會預計將重啟對美歐貿易協議的表決程序。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU to Suspend Planned Counter Tariffs on €93 Billion of US Goods</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%B0%87%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E5%B0%8D930%E5%84%84%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-154735113.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-24 01:46:02",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國1月消費者信心升至五個月高位 受訪者對經濟和自身財務更加樂觀",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"University of Michigan\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"728\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5yV6jAxbw_WI1tM4XwfpTg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/47fdd184e1e42b6293bf40786df3b076\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">University of Michigan</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國消費者信心在1月份升至5個月高位，因美國人對經濟和自身財務狀況的樂觀情緒上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:密西根大學;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/密西根大學\">密西根大學</a>數據顯示，1月份消費者信心指數終值較上月上升3.5點，達到56.4，高於初值讀數。該數據也超過了接受彭博調查的所有經濟學家的預測值。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LbkLqsMZj8TI0JsXlga4XQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/72b5fa10e684ab63a9662d09d6cb9bc4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1月份消費者信心指數的月度上升幅度為6月份以來最大，並反映出不同收入、年齡、教育程度和政治立場群體的普遍改善。密西根大學稱，受訪者自發提及關稅的比例連續5個月下降。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fd61bbf0-0bfb-3341-883b-3efd6c660896-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，密西根大學負責該調查的主任Joanne Hsu在聲明中表示，「全國消費者信心仍較1年前低逾20%，消費者仍在報告高物價以及勞動力市場可能走弱對其購買力造成壓力。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五公佈的數據顯示，消費者預計未來1年價格將上漲4%，為2025年1月份以來最低。他們對未來5至10年的通膨預期為3.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管對高物價感到沮喪，消費者支出依然展現韌性並推動經濟成長。對許多美國人而言，退稅也可能有助於緩解對家庭財務狀況的一些焦慮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衡量個人財務預期的一項指標在本月升至接近1年來最高水平。對當前家庭財務狀況的看法也有所改善。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衡量總體預期的指數升至6個月高位，而對當前狀況的評估指數則從12月份的紀錄低位回升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hsu表示，儘管消費者可能對近期國際局勢發展有看法，但「他們似乎並不認為這會對其個人財務或更廣泛的美國經濟帶來顯著影響」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本次調查期涵蓋12月16日至1月19日的受訪者回覆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Consumer Sentiment Rises to Five-Month High in Broad Advance</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Maria Paula Mijares Torres.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B1%E6%9C%88%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%94%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D-%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8D%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E6%9B%B4%E5%8A%A0%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80-153213490.html",
